You buy this little purple bottle 

One thing I cannot and will not try to afford is extensions, one thing I can afford is this little purple bottle!

My extensions in a bottle! Easy to install and they last a life time… literally! 

This isn’t just any scalp serum. This water based serum leaves you non greasy, and the ingredients is really what works! 

Melatonin plays a role in hair growth by increasing the proliferation of hair follicle cells and promoting the anagen (growth) phase of the hair cycle. Clinical studies have proven that topical application of melatonin may improve hair density and thickness in as little as 60-90 days. 

Caffeine, on the other hand, may stimulate hair growth by blocking the effects of DHT, a hormone that can cause hair loss in both men and women. Caffeine also improve blood circulation to the scalp, which can help deliver nutrients and oxygen to the hair follicles.

When combined, these two ingredients make the perfect feeding grounds for new hair growth and thicker and healthier hair.

My hair use to be so thin and fragile, and now it’s safe to say it’s the strongest and healthiest it’s ever been.
